Package wargame.map

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnimationHandler
    The aim of this class is to load the animations and contain them.
    Map
    This class represents two sets of MapElement associated to their position.
    MapElement
    This class represent an element of the map: the ground, a tree, water spot, etc
    It also defines if we can cross it, shot through, etc.
    MapGenerator
    This class generates a map, using the map generator parameter.
    MapGeneratorParameter
    This class defined the parameters used by the map generator to generate a map.
    RockShape
    Defines a rock set shape.
    Shape
    Represents a shape.
    Spot
    Represent a spot (a tree, a forest, ...) with its position and dimensions.
    SpriteHandler
    The aim of this class is to load the sprites and contain them.
    TreeShape
    Defines a tree set shape.
    WaterShape
    Defines a water set shape.
